properties.Name: FastaNucleicAcidCode
properties.Description:
The nucleic acid codes used by the FASTA file format.

A --> adenosine          
M --> A C (amino)
C --> cytidine            
S --> G C (strong)
G --> guanine             
W --> A T (weak)
T --> thymidine           
B --> G T C
U --> uridine            
 D --> G A T R --> G A (purine)       
 H --> A C T
Y --> T C (pyrimidine)    
V --> G C A K --> G T (keto)         
 N --> A G C T (any)
